><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/2b23ae001626066e4aac3f4ded00e3ff.poster.avif?t=1762307614\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/2b23ae001626066e4aac3f4ded00e3ff.webm?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/2b23ae001626066e4aac3f4ded00e3ff.mp4?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel like you can beat your own score? Wanna brag about your  efficiency in your local community? Challenge yourself to see if you can beat your previous records!</p>",
